<small> *'''Easy Installation''' - Plug the adapter into an available PCI Express slot to upgrade desktop *'''Hi-Speed Wi-Fi''' - Up to 1.9Gbps (1300Mbps on 5GHz band or 600Mpbs on 2.4GHz band) *'''802.11ac Dual Band''' - 3 times faster than the 802.11n standard, perfect for network usage *'''Beamforming Technology''' - Receives more directional Wi-Fi signals, speed and reliability *'''Ultimate Range''' - 3 external antennas ensure a range of Wi-Fi connection and stability *'''Backward Compatibility''' - With support for 802.11a/b/g/n standards </small>
